main event: A group of approximately 30 students observed a round-shaped white object moving from south to north multiple times on 14 Mar 67.
interesting points: The object had different colored lights and was seen flying due south in an arc., The sighting lasted about 5 minutes., The weather at the time was foggy/misty with a low ceiling., There were several aircraft in the area during the sighting., Two students had previously reported similar sightings on the same date.
witness description: students at the University of Wisconsin
